CHANGES
=======

0.5.4
-----

* reformatted codebase
* sa\_path now raises the correct errors
* sa\_number and sa\_string now raise the correct errors
* sa\_int and sa\_list now raise the correct errors
* sa\_float now raises correct errors
* Replaced all self.assertRaises(Exception)'s with the correct TypeError or ValueError errors
* Updated all tests to expect TypeError instead of Exception when testing for type
* replaced assertions in base\_rule
* sa\_bool now also uses the new abstract base class

0.5.3
-----

* circumvented the circular dependencies, created issue 24 'Remove circular dependency' in Github
* added base rule and refactored all existing rules to use the abstract rule

0.5.2
-----

* fixed test\_none\_kwargs\_allow\_none tests
* added tests for all rules regarding the usage of default values for kwargs and when allow\_none is set to True
* added test\_use\_default\_if\_none to sa\_int
* Updated setup.cfg to use new summary

0.5.1
-----

* reversed changes to correct and incorrect int c in application test
* updated test\_application to use required kwargs
* Updated rules to check for kwargs and args
* added required kwargs tests to other rules
* added kwargs to signature preserving tests
* sa\_int now works with kwargs
* added tests for sa\_int with required kwargs

0.5.0
-----

* Added 'signature-preserving' to the readme rst

0.4.5
-----

* moved utils to appropriate test directory and renamed it to test\_utils

0.4.4
-----

* removed rules submodule

0.4.3
-----

* added \_all\_\_ to pytsa.py

0.4.2
-----

* updated travis yml to install requirements.txt and test\_requirements.txt
* Finished application test
* implemented temporary fix for test\_args\_name\_missing and created new issue for it in github
* all rules now use the new @decorator to preserve their signature
* added requirements.txt and added keep signature test for every rule
* started new implementation using decorator dependency
* added new test class

0.4.1
-----

* readded blank line at start of document
* Update coveralls badge image url
* Added coveralls badge
* added code coverage to travis.yml

